[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "触碰到海岛洞窟深处的传送门的瞬间，耀眼的白光笼罩了瑟瑞斯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "恒沙的防御系统解除了吗？分析员和其他人怎么样了？下一个小世界又会是什么样？这些念头在瑟瑞斯的脑中一闪而过。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "回过神时，瑟瑞斯发觉自己站在人来人往的街道上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "又在发呆？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "瑟瑞斯看着面前的人摸了摸她的头，又朝她伸出手。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 1,
        "Speaker": "？？？",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "该走了哦？再磨磨蹭蹭本小姐可不等你们了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 2,
        "Speaker": "？？？",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "大家——下次再来新恒提罗玩呀！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 3,
        "Speaker": "？？？",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "会的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "虽然看不清，但瑟瑞斯感觉到每个人的脸上都挂着笑容，那个人的掌心也如过去那般温暖。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "远方，众人即将搭乘的空艇已经着陆，机器人和空港工人正来回奔走着卸下货物。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "瑟瑞斯一边走，一边想着，原来事情都已经解决了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "自己怎么把这么重要的事情都忘了呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "天空是灰色的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女从满是灰尘的废墟上爬起，慢慢地向前走。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在不久前，这座城市被毁掉了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她被埋在了研究所的残骸之下，不知过了多久。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女觉得，她弄丢了什么很重要的东西。",
        "disable": 0
    },
