        "Flag": "b-1-3-0",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女什么都想不起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "b-1-3-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她觉得自己属于这里，但这里并不接纳她。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "？？？",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这里什么都没有留下。已经没有必要在这里停留了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "列车微微摇晃着，少女独自坐在柔软的座椅上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她不知道这班列车会开往哪里，但随着列车摇晃的身体给了她些许自己真实存在的安全感。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "列车上的广播始终重复播放着什么，但少女一句也听不懂，这令她感到烦躁。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "？？？",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只要忘掉就不会有烦恼了。",
